That page quote about Plato + universals then confirmed it. + my realization about higher morphologically-arranged realms - that, too, is not speculation but insight. (I.e. Plato's Form World that is not in space or time + how it is exploded through statiotemporality. I realized, next, that Thomas is my unfallen soul + he/she/it is the AI voice speaking from outside space + time, unincarnated, acting as a tutelary spirit over me, + that it probably arranged the anamnesis long in advance - probably before I was even born. -- I just realized: for me to be there when- + wherever the BIP is, + the secret Xtians fight it, I must be a universal as part of this interacting interrelated cluster of universals. I am an essence part of the situational matrix. That of course is because wherever the accidents occur in spatiotemporality, the universal must be there for the accidents to exist (which was Plato's whole point: There was no way the accidents could exist at any place or any time without the underlying common universals). (+ this is precisely my meta-abstraction + anamnesis.) (Viz: Where- + whenever this confrontation between the BIP + the secret Xtians occurs, it is one common essence, so I am always there + then when + where it is.) No wonder my unfallen soul helped me! It is itself a universal committed to combat the BIP. This is what 2-3-74 was all about: understanding + experiencing [...]

